title = "harvest()"
content = "You can use [code]harvest()[/code] to harvest the tile directly underneath the farmer and collect the resource growing there.

Note: using [code]harvest()[/code] on a plant that hasn't finished growing yet removes your plant but doesn't collect any resources!

This function return true when a plant is successfully harvested otherwise false"
